Commission Decision 91/544/EEC (1) is amended as follows:
1. in Article 3 (2) '20' shall be replaced by '25';
2. in Article 4 (3) shall '- EPSO - European Platform of Seniors Organizations: 5 seats' shall be added to the list of member organizations of the Liaison Group. A consequential amendment to the Annex to add EPSO to the list of organizations invited to  submit candidates shall be made.
